description: Andrey builds web applications for about 8 years, and he is an active member of JavaScript, Node, and Mozilla Rust communities in Ukraine. He speaks at conferences, does trainings, takes part in coding competitions and hackathons, and co-hosts Frontend UA hangout. Currently Andrey works at DataRobot - a data science company in Kiev, Ukraine.
title: #RSConf - Ember = Angular = React, Андрей Листочкин
